'''Vil''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] student at the [[University of Agamar]]. In [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], he was one of the members of Dr. [[Anki Pace]]'s team that made a research trip to [[Bimmiel/Legends|Bimmiel]].

He and [[Denna]] were captured by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] and placed in the [[Embrace of Pain]]. Fortunately for the pair, both he and Denna were rescued by [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] and [[Ganner Rhysode]] shortly thereafter.

